'''Rhubarb''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Rhubarb Seeds]] after 13 days. Rhubarb seeds can be purchased only from the [[Oasis]], or occasionally from the [[Traveling Cart]].

